title: Anthony and Helen of "Goblin Works Garage"
description:
Anthony Partridge is a a fabricator and host on Goblin Works Garage, a show that airs on Discovery, where they build wild cars and bikes.

Check out their show! https://watch.motortrend.com/tv-shows/goblin-works-garage/about

This show is also a video: https://youtu.be/zRLghIlPCm0
